ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: PHIL 706 is a seminar in which advanced philosophy graduate students meet with each other to present and receive feedback on their work (from their peers and from the course's instructors).

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course deepened my knowledge of the profession by exposing me to a number of new philosophical problems and arguments.This course contributed to my dissertation research because I received some very valuable feedback on a paper based on it.
